@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_rtwofd(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = tmp
    v2 = v1
    v1 = wp.cos(((v0 + 0.80 * v2 + 0.25) - (tmp + 0.26 * v0 + 0.13)))
    v2 = (wp.sin((v2 + 0.17 + tmp + 0.31)) * (wp.exp(v2 + 0.20) + wp.exp(tmp + 0.73)))
    v2 = v2
    data[tid] = v0
